  "description": "<b>近日，来自英国巴斯大学的研究人员通过结合纳米针技术和原子力显微技术，研发出了一种可建造3D人体皮肤模型的方法。</b>这将对皮肤病和皮肤老化问题的研究起到重要作用。截止到目前为止，研究人员只能通过原子显微技术分析角质细胞表层。现在，在探针尾端加入纳米针之后，将可检测到表层下的物质。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d43b398/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241066.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%BA%B3%E7%B1%B3%E9%92%88%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241066.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%BA%B3%E7%B1%B3%E9%92%88%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241066.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%BA%B3%E7%B1%B3%E9%92%88%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241066.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E7%BA%B3%E7%B1%B3%E9%92%88%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241066.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E